description: Golden crunchy crumbed fish, zingy kiwifruit and chilli create a flavour explosion in your mouth in these terrific fish tacos. Try these for dinner tonight.
keywords: Crumbed Fish Tacos With Kiwifruit Salsa
name: Crumbed Fish Tacos With Kiwifruit Salsa Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 tbs Woolworths extra virgin olive oil

recipeInstructions.text: Place cabbage and remaining vinegar and oil in a separate medium bowl and toss to coat. Season with pepper. Serve tortillas topped with cabbage, kiwifruit salsa, fish fingers and avocado.
